706543f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ryder Avenue - Avenue S
706543f-a.text:
Ryder Ave., at the S.W. corner of Ave. S., sho ing the home of
E.H. Ryder from 1860-1873. E. Ryder was owner in 1857, and in 1922 one
Hill was the occupant.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

706542f-b.text:

Ryder ave., at the S.W. corner of Ave. S., showing the hone of E.
Ryder (1857) and E.H. Ryder (1860-1873). It was occupied by one Hill
in 1922. This houee.in the Brooklyn Atlas of 1929,is in East 29th
Street, just south of Ave. S., and will either be moved or demolished at
a subsequent date.
